name: Logger Pro Data File
summary: Learn about .CMBL files and view a list of programs that open them.

windows.name: Open over 400 file formats with File Viewer Plus.Free Download

content: CMBL files are used to record and measure data during lab experiments for homework or class-related problems. While the Graphical Analysis iOS app can import most data from the CMBL file, it cannot import calculated columns from the file.

description: File created by Logger Pro, a program that allows students to collect and analyze data in science and math education programs; contains spreadseet data, data analysis, and movies recorded during a scientific experiment or exercise.
